ze","Recently I hit a TypeError when using sequelize-cli — \"The 'data' argument must be one of type string, TypedArray, or DataView. Received type number\". Here's a quick note on the cause.",{"url":45,"title":46,"date":47,"updated":3,"category":12,"tags":48,"description":49,"readingMinutes":23},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2019\u002F07\u002F18\u002Fkoa-saga-mysql-sequelize-2\u002F","Koa Saga: MySQL — sequelize (2)","2019-07-18 13:50:28",[5,14],"We've connected to the DB. Now let's insert data.",{"url":51,"title":52,"date":53,"updated":3,"category":12,"tags":54,"description":55,"readingMinutes":16},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2019\u002F07\u002F17\u002Fkoa-saga-mysql-sequelize-1\u002F","Koa Saga: MySQL — sequelize (1)","2019-07-17 14:37:47",[5,14],"Time to use sequelize — an ORM that helps with things like SQL injection.",{"url":57,"title":58,"date":59,"updated":3,"category":12,"tags":60,"description":61,"readingMinutes":16},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2019\u002F07\u002F17\u002Fkoa-saga-mysql-sql-injection\u002F","Koa Saga: MySQL — SQL Injection","2019-07-17 08:40:05",[5,14],"After basic SQL, let's talk about SQL injection — what it is and why it's dangerous.",{"url":63,"title":64,"date":65,"updated":3,"category":12,"tags":66,"description":67,"readingMinutes":16},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2019\u002F07\u002F16\u002Fkoa-saga-mysql-basics-3\u002F","Koa Saga: MySQL Basics (3)","2019-07-16 10:09:57",[5,14],"This post covers CRUD SQL commands — slightly more involved. SELECT was already covered in the previous post.",{"url":69,"title":70,"date":71,"updated":3,"category":12,"tags":72,"description":73,"readingMinutes":16},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2019\u002F07\u002F15\u002Fkoa-saga-mysql-basics-2\u002F","Koa Saga: MySQL Basics (2)","2019-07-15 10:35:15",[5,14],"We've got MySQL ready. Now let me use a DB management tool to operate on it.",178,18,{"postCount":77,"tagCount":78},1034,1042,1784012789638]